OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThere will
OL,6,Fbe a mixture of clear intervals and
OL,7,Fshowers, these more frequent over the
OL,8,FNorthwest Highlands in the evening and
OL,9,Fearly night. Brisk southwesterly winds
OL,10,Fin the far northwest easing down.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FBright or sunny spells and a
OL,13,Ffew scattered showers, these more
OL,14,Ffrequent in the far northwest. Drier
OL,15,Fin the east. Rather cool.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FSunny
OL,18,Fintervals and scattered showers on
OL,19,FSaturday. Cloudy with outbreaks of
OL,20,Frain spreading in on Sunday. Brighter
OL,21,Fwith a few showers on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
